Sonry FR7 CGI command relay to relay comands form non digest authentucation enabled clients (companion)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL

Navigate to your project folder
mkdir ~/digest-relay
cd ~/digest-relay

Initialize a Node.js project
npm init -y

Install Required Packages
npm install express body-parser digest-fetch

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Usage

for example to send 

http://192.168.50.51/command/ptzf.cgi?FocusPushAFMF=press
 
use

curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/relay \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "ip": "192.168.50.51",
    "path": "ptzf.cgi",
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "password",
    "query": "FocusPushAFMF=press"
  }'



